## AUTH STATE RULES [NEW v4]

The app has THREE auth states. ALWAYS handle all three:

```typescript
// In any component that needs to know auth state:
const { session, isGuest, guestUuid } = useAuthStore();

// Three-state pattern:
if (isLoading) { /* show nothing or skeleton */ }
if (session) { /* authenticated behaviour */ }
if (isGuest) { /* guest behaviour — never block, use SoftAuthGateModal for gated actions */ }
```

### When to show SoftAuthGateModal:
- Guest taps Save/bookmark icon on any venue card
- Guest taps "Get Tickets" CTA
- Guest taps "Report an Issue" button

### When NOT to use SoftAuthGateModal:
- Guest browsing ExploreScreen, MapScreen, SearchScreen
- Guest viewing VenueDetailScreen content (images, notes, hours, map)
- Guest tapping Share button (sharing is always allowed)

### Guest UUID management:
```typescript
// CORRECT — read from MMKV via useAuthStore
const { guestUuid } = useAuthStore();

// WRONG — never generate UUID in a component
const id = uuidv4(); // Only useAuthStore.initGuest() may do this
```

---

## DATA FETCHING RULES

Every Supabase call must follow this exact pattern:

```typescript
// src/features/explore/hooks/useVenues.ts
import { useQuery } from '@tanstack/react-query';
import { supabase } from '@/lib/supabase';
import { QUERY_KEYS } from '@/constants/queryKeys';
import type { Venue } from '@/types';

export const useVenues = (categoryId?: string) => {
  return useQuery({
    queryKey: [QUERY_KEYS.VENUES, categoryId],
    queryFn: async (): Promise<Venue[]> => {
      let query = supabase
        .from('venues')
        .select('*, categories(*), venue_updates(*)')
        .eq('is_active', true)
        .order('created_at', { ascending: false });

      if (categoryId) query = query.eq('category_id', categoryId);

      const { data, error } = await query;
      if (error) throw new Error(error.message);
      return data ?? [];
    },
    staleTime: 1000 * 60 * 5,
    gcTime: 1000 * 60 * 30,
    retry: 3,
  });
};
```

---

## STATE MANAGEMENT RULES

- **Zustand** = session, auth loading, `isGuest`, `guestUuid`, UI toggles, theme
- **TanStack Query** = all server data (venues, categories, profile from DB)
- **MMKV** = local persistence (recently viewed, onboarding seen, theme, `guest_uuid`)

```typescript
// STORAGE_KEYS — the only valid MMKV keys:
export const STORAGE_KEYS = {
  RECENTLY_VIEWED: 'recentlyViewed',
  RECENT_SEARCHES: 'recentSearches',
  ONBOARDING_SEEN: 'hasSeenOnboarding',
  USER_THEME: 'userTheme',
  GUEST_UUID: 'guest_uuid',         // [NEW v4] NEVER regenerate once set
} as const;
```

---

## COMPONENT RULES

### List rendering:
```tsx
// ALWAYS — for any list of venues or categories
import { FlashList } from '@shopify/flash-list';

<FlashList
  data={venues}
  renderItem={({ item }) => <VenueCard venue={item} />}
  estimatedItemSize={280}
  keyExtractor={(item) => item.id}
  onEndReached={fetchNextPage}
  onEndReachedThreshold={0.5}
/>
```

### Image rendering:
```tsx
// ALWAYS — never use RN's built-in Image
import { Image } from 'expo-image';

<Image
  source={{ uri: venue.images?.[0] ?? PLACEHOLDER_IMAGE_URL }}
  placeholder="LKN]Rv%2Tw=w]~U@D*I=x]x]v~E8"
  contentFit="cover"
  transition={200}
  cachePolicy="memory-disk"
  style={styles.image}
/>
```

### Bottom sheets (modals):
```tsx
// ALWAYS — use react-native-bottom-sheet, never Modal from react-native
import BottomSheet, { BottomSheetBackdrop } from '@gorhom/bottom-sheet';

const ref = useRef<BottomSheet>(null);

<BottomSheet
  ref={ref}
  snapPoints={['40%']}
  backdropComponent={BottomSheetBackdrop}
  backgroundStyle={{ backgroundColor: theme.colors.surfaceHighest }}
  handleIndicatorStyle={{ backgroundColor: theme.colors.onSurfaceVariant }}
>
  {/* Modal content */}
</BottomSheet>
```

### Every screen must handle these states:
```tsx
const { data, isLoading, isError, refetch } = useVenues();

if (isLoading) return <SkeletonList />;
if (isError) return <OfflineState onRetry={refetch} />;
if (!data?.length) return <EmptyState message="No venues here yet" />;
```

### VenueCard bookmark button — guest check:
```tsx
// CORRECT — check isGuest before mutation
const { isGuest } = useAuthStore();
const [showGate, setShowGate] = useState(false);

const handleBookmark = () => {
  if (isGuest) {
    setShowGate(true); // Opens SoftAuthGateModal
    Analytics.softGateTriggered('save_venue', venue.id, isGuest, guestUuid);
    return;
  }
  toggleSave.mutate(!isSaved);
};
```

